// 芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓 USERS 芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓芒鈥濃偓
model User {
  id                Int            @id @default(autoincrement())
  nomeCompleto      String         @map("nome_completo") @db.VarChar(255)
  email             String         @unique @db.VarChar(255)
  cpf               String?        @db.VarChar(11)
  telefone          String?        @db.VarChar(20)
  senha             String         @db.VarChar(255)
  saldo             Decimal        @default(0) @db.Decimal(10, 2)
  saldoDemo         Decimal        @default(0) @map("saldo_demo") @db.Decimal(10, 2)
  saldoRevshare     Decimal        @default(0) @map("saldo_revshare") @db.Decimal(10, 2)
  affiliateCode     String?        @unique @map("affiliate_code") @db.VarChar(50)
  comissao          Int            @default(10)
  referredById      Int?           @map("referred_by")
  role              Role           @default(user)
  commissionType    CommissionType @default(rev) @map("commission_type")
  cpaValue          Decimal        @default(10) @map("cpa_value") @db.Decimal(10, 2)
  isInfluencer      Boolean        @default(false) @map("is_influencer")
  managerId         Int?           @map("manager_id")
  managerPool       Decimal        @default(0) @map("manager_pool") @db.Decimal(5, 2)
  revshareRecurring Boolean        @default(true) @map("revshare_recurring")
  managerRecurring  Boolean        @default(true) @map("manager_recurring")
  withdrawTaxPaid   Boolean        @default(false) @map("withdraw_tax_paid")
  status            UserStatus     @default(offline)
  lastSeen          DateTime?      @map("last_seen")
  createdAt         DateTime       @default(now()) @map("created_at")
  updatedAt         DateTime       @updatedAt @map("updated_at")

  referredBy             User?                 @relation("UserReferrals", fields: [referredById], references: [id])
  referrals              User[]                @relation("UserReferrals")
  manager                User?                 @relation("ManagerInfluencers", fields: [managerId], references: [id])
  influencers            User[]                @relation("ManagerInfluencers")
  deposits               Deposit[]
  withdrawals            Withdrawal[]
  gameHistory            GameHistory[]
  affiliateLogsGiven     AffiliateLog[]        @relation("AffiliateReferrer")
  affiliateLogsReceived  AffiliateLog[]        @relation("AffiliateReferred")
  campaignsCreated       InfluencerCampaign[]
  campaignParticipations CampaignParticipant[]
  rolloverCampaigns      RolloverCampaign[]

  @@map("users")
}

enum Role {
  user
  manager
  admin
}

enum CommissionType {
  rev
  cpa
}

enum UserStatus {
  online
  offline
}

